responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "B632F253480FD0F88E0FF1BB0CEE39F4", "Come and dance final sister of Sephillion. Dance the dance and wish for me. Melayna, eldest and most wise. What wonders do you wish to see? Father of mine and curator of curses I would wish my sisters returned to me.")
